TITLE: Starting Preview Server with Vike API in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to use the preview() function to start a preview server using the production build. It demonstrates handling the returned viteConfig and viteServer values.
SOURCE: https://github.com/vikejs/vike/blob/main/docs/pages/api/+Page.mdx#2025-04-17_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import { preview } from 'vike/api'
const {
  viteConfig, // Resolved Vite configuration
  viteServer, // Vite's development server
} = await preview({
  viteConfig // Vite configuration (optional)
})
