TITLE: Configuring Permanent Redirections in Vike
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to set up permanent redirections (HTTP status code 301) in a Vike project. It includes examples of simple redirects, parameterized redirections, glob redirections, and external redirections.
SOURCE: https://github.com/vikejs/vike/blob/main/docs/pages/redirects/+Page.mdx#2025-04-17_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
// pages/+config.js

export default {
  redirects: {
    '/about-us': '/about',
    // Parameterized redirections
    '/product/@id': '/buy/@id',
    // Glob redirections
    '/admin/*': '/private/*',
    // External redirections
    '/admin/*': 'https://admin.example.org/*'
  }
}
```

