TITLE: Implementing onRenderClient Hook for SPA in Vike
DESCRIPTION: This code demonstrates how to implement the onRenderClient hook for SPA pages, using a UI framework's renderToDom method to render the page in the browser.
SOURCE: https://github.com/vikejs/vike/blob/main/docs/pages/render-modes/+Page.mdx#2025-04-17_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
// /renderer/+onRenderClient.js
// Environment: browser

import { renderToDom } from 'some-ui-framework'

export { onRenderClient }

async function onRenderClient(pageContext) {
  const { Page } = pageContext
  // UI frameworks usually have two methods, such as `renderToDom()` and `hydrateDom()`.
  // Note how we use `renderToDom()` and not `hydrateDom()`.
  await renderToDom(document.getElementById('root'), Page)
}
```

