TITLE: Updating server integration with pageRender
DESCRIPTION: Changes how pageRender is called in server integration points, moving from passing url as a parameter to setting it as a property on the pageContext object before calling pageRender.
SOURCE: https://github.com/vikejs/vike/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md#2025-04-17_snippet_21

LANGUAGE: diff
CODE:
```
  // At your server integration point

  const express = require('express')
  const { createPageRender } = require('vite-plugin-ssr')

  /* ... */

  const pageRender = createPageRender(/*...*/)

  /* ... */

- pageRender({ url, pageContext })
+ pageContext.url = url
+ pageRender(pageContext)
```

