TITLE: Breaking Change: Page Render Function Update
DESCRIPTION: Shows updates to the page rendering API and response handling.
SOURCE: https://github.com/vikejs/vike/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md#2025-04-17_snippet_16

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
  const renderPage = createPageRenderer(/*...*/)
  app.get('*', async (req, res, next) => {
    const url = req.originalUrl
-   const pageContext = { url }
-   const result = await renderPage(pageContext)
-   if (result.nothingRendered) return next()
-   res.status(result.statusCode).send(result.renderResult)
+   const pageContextInit = { url }
+   const pageContext = await renderPage(pageContextInit)
+   if (!pageContext.httpResponse) return next()
+   res.status(pageContext.httpResponse.statusCode).send(pageContext.httpResponse.body)
  })
```

