TITLE: Identifying the Root Cause of 'Cannot read properties of undefined' Error
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet illustrates the underlying issue causing the 'Cannot read properties of undefined' error. It shows how CJS/ESM issues can lead to undefined imports, resulting in runtime errors when accessing properties.
SOURCE: https://github.com/vikejs/vike/blob/main/docs/pages/broken-npm-package/+Page.mdx#2025-04-17_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
// node_modules/some-good-lib/dist/index.js

// Because of CJS/ESM issues, someImport is undefined
import { someImport } from 'some-broken-lib'

// ...

function someFunction() {
  // TypeError: Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'someProp')
  someImport.someProp
}
```

